CatDescriptText: Ruth Tucker is the mother of Mary Jane Page and Virginia Goggins is her aunt.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men and women in Egyptian or North African costumes, including Mildred, standing third from left, Mary Ellen, second row, second from left, Ruth Tucker, fourth from right, and Virginia Goggins, seated in center, with Mrs. Hightower,  Mildred Brown, and Hazel Bradfordsome with Shriners Sahara fez, in room with table with sign for Kay Boys' Club
